{"word":"κτεατίζω","slug":"κτεατίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κτεατίζω</b></el> <el>(κτεᾰτίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κτάομαι'><el>κτάομαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>to get, gain, win</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, <i>to get for oneself, acquire</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}